{"tid":2108974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主黨副主席羅健熙今早被警方上門拘捕","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T02:18:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3240f43b5e15e81f544c73b3a65a8fca39a97ec","tid":2108974,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:14:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537789-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537789-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=9d47c237\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537789-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1ae95502\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537789-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨表示，副主席羅健熙今早6時半被警方上門拘捕，相信與去年11月18日理工大學外的案件有關。民主黨批評警方為求政治目的不講理由，已聯絡律師團隊協助羅健熙。<br />\n<br />\n羅健熙去年11月18日在距離理工大學超過500米的幸福中心被捕，現場當時有另外數十人被捕。"},{"pid":"36d7c7f6a3820a4b1d22db20e1a108c2d2817d40","tid":2108974,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"Twitter"}]}